Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.56,0:00:04.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向聯邦軍全體將士通話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.20,0:00:09.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們即將開始進攻敵人要塞拉·格拉密斯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.64,0:00:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AGE-FX的新模式調試已經完成
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.10,0:00:16.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字叫FX Buster模式
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.40,0:00:21.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中央的敵人艦隊是假像
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.46,0:00:23.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命令全軍散開！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.28,0:00:26.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德雷克
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.08,0:00:33.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人要塞炮為補充能量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.77,0:00:35.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下次發射前有一定間隔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.94,0:00:37.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中央突破！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.22,0:00:40.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天神號 最大戰速
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.23,0:00:46.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…不是什麼誤射
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.46,0:00:48.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薩那倫多的部隊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.17,0:00:52.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏就是你們的墳墓
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.89,0:00:57.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二波攻擊隊 出擊！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.46,0:00:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就等著這一刻呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.51,0:01:01.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天要為他們報仇雪恨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.60,0:01:05.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狄恩·亞農
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.66,0:01:06.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jerspin 出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.61,0:01:25.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.11,0:01:33.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機動戰士嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.84,0:01:38.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪兒 高達！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.92,0:02:07.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裏來的怪物 怎麼還有這種機體
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.48,0:02:10.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鎮靜 它看似威力強大
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.54,0:02:11.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但武器好像
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.67,0:02:13.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅限於前端的螺旋狀光束炮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.20,0:02:15.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉向能力也差
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.46,0:02:18.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要冷靜應對 不會是個可怕的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.11,0:02:35.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝幫忙 船長
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.83,0:02:40.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新型機？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.40,0:02:54.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,X-R部隊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.72,0:03:02.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露烏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.25,0:03:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會帶你去地球
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.00,0:03:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶你去看…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.63,0:03:10.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚮往的地球
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.57,0:03:12.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.70,0:05:00.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人艦艇 迅速到位
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.20,0:05:04.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要塞方向 正在形成一道防線
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.65,0:05:07.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人艦隊側翼突襲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.15,0:05:09.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.48,0:05:11.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優先支援天神號
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.83,0:05:12.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.67,0:05:14.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用來提醒我戰況嚴峻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.18,0:05:17.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 如不形成突破口
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.82,0:05:19.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們沒有勝算
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.73,0:05:25.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.67,0:05:28.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為打破眼下的局勢 只有這一個辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.07,0:05:31.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都聽見了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.64,0:05:34.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用光子爆破炮在敵人陣型上打開大洞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.74,0:05:35.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那裏突擊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.38,0:05:40.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其後 成功突破的艦艇集中火力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.59,0:05:43.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接攻擊敵人要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.23,0:05:45.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長 傳令下去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.06,0:05:48.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 光子爆破炮準備發射
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.94,0:05:52.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發射後 向敵人宇宙要塞發起突擊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.30,0:05:53.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.41,0:05:57.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿比斯隊全體聽令
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.80,0:05:59.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優先保護天神號
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.42,0:06:00.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.56,0:06:07.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底想幹什麼 薩那倫多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.48,0:06:10.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然敢向我開火
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.49,0:06:12.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是您誤會了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.81,0:06:16.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是您在錯誤的時間出現在錯誤的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.18,0:06:17.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.96,0:06:20.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們其實也非常遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.97,0:06:25.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是您的在場 可以擊落更多敵機
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.17,0:06:28.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒聽見我的命令嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.49,0:06:31.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中央區域不得部署艦隊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.49,0:06:32.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少自大了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.95,0:06:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從沒把你看作是伊澤爾坎特大人的繼承人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.77,0:06:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪格瑪Xenon炮已經不能發射
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.70,0:06:44.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們將根據戰況獨自行動
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.52,0:06:46.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來 薩那倫多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.08,0:06:51.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薩那倫多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.09,0:06:54.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想和我作對到底嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.62,0:07:10.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對手的行動太不規則
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.94,0:07:32.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停止這種戰鬥方式 吉歐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.24,0:07:35.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒看到剛才的慘狀嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.49,0:07:52.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到你了 高達！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.07,0:07:55.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉歐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.64,0:08:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下意識擋住了 值得誇獎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.45,0:08:08.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但能招架到何時呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.07,0:08:12.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格拉德和戴蒙要你去死！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.48,0:08:20.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舍利奇隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.98,0:08:23.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天神號在被敵人機動戰士攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.80,0:08:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去護衛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.23,0:08:25.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.21,0:08:29.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道怎麼對付那東西 你快去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.28,0:08:33.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.75,0:08:39.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我恨你 為什麼來礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.15,0:08:42.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真像是當鬥牛士的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.11,0:08:45.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是別想繼續橫衝直撞了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.76,0:08:55.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我教你的不是殺人手段
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.64,0:08:57.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是在戰場上求生的辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.57,0:09:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是伊澤爾坎特大人的兒子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.36,0:09:03.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你長得簡直和他像極了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.08,0:09:04.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好美
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.10,0:09:08.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球一定比這裏更美吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.95,0:09:11.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想去看看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.01,0:09:17.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望維甘和地球人都活得更好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.83,0:09:20.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.25,0:09:31.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 該死 該死
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.69,0:09:34.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那台機體的攻擊方式太單一了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.60,0:09:41.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要瞭解它的攻擊方式
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.93,0:09:44.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威力再大也不足為懼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.12,0:09:47.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我怎麼能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.60,0:09:50.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敗在高達以外的機體手裏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.04,0:09:56.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放出這招以後
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.73,0:09:58.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是個活動靶子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.15,0:10:07.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.23,0:10:13.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於讓我逮住你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.36,0:10:16.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你知道大言不慚的下場
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.98,0:10:20.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接碾成肉罐頭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.14,0:10:22.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.74,0:10:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經將死你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.91,0:10:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優先供應維生系統
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.00,0:10:54.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦內多處顯示受損
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.10,0:10:57.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過主要動力系統還在運轉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.77,0:10:59.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光子爆破炮進入最終發射程序
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.41,0:11:02.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發射準備即將完成
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.41,0:11:05.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 命令射線軸上友軍退避
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.78,0:11:08.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 探測系統有反應
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.26,0:11:11.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人艦艇上發現友軍識別信號
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.63,0:11:14.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是舍利奇隊長的機體
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.69,0:11:30.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼情況
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.31,0:11:33.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天神號在磨蹭什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.32,0:11:37.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說是 射線軸上的敵艦附近
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.17,0:11:38.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有我軍機體被困
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.62,0:11:40.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法自行脫離
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.61,0:11:41.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.35,0:11:46.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舍利奇隊長 舍利奇隊長 請回答
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.53,0:11:48.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舍利奇隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.91,0:11:51.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光子爆破炮已經完成發射準備
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.56,0:11:54.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請盡快離開那裏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.26,0:11:55.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,駕駛員狀況如何
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.92,0:11:57.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通訊系統運轉正常
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.54,0:11:58.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舍利奇少校
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.85,0:12:00.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請回答 少校
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.36,0:12:09.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天…天神號嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.60,0:12:10.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少校！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.02,0:12:13.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光子爆破炮發射在即
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.98,0:12:16.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你立刻離開那裏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.87,0:12:29.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了 完全動不了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.21,0:12:32.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就…從駕駛艙逃生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.50,0:12:35.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外殼好像已經被撞得變形了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.97,0:12:39.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒法… 一個人打開
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.31,0:12:40.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.49,0:12:43.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,納圖爾艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.61,0:12:46.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用管我 發射
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.23,0:12:50.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該非常清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.45,0:12:53.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一擊的重要性
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.54,0:12:57.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該死 快讓開！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.07,0:12:59.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長 隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.58,0:13:08.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快…機會轉瞬即逝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.86,0:13:10.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人開始規避
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.70,0:13:12.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命令附近部隊前往救援
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.51,0:13:16.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛發出撤離命令 周圍無人可派
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.79,0:13:23.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左舷8區顯示受損
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.96,0:13:26.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷害控制三班 前往受損區域
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.99,0:13:29.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去的話 天神號也難保
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.59,0:13:31.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到那時候 聯邦…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.23,0:13:33.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.17,0:13:38.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 可是！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.04,0:13:42.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了 艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.93,0:14:05.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舍利奇少校
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.19,0:14:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感謝…你所做的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.59,0:14:14.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舍利奇·阿比斯 結束通訊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.00,0:14:16.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝貴艦好運
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.23,0:14:25.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光子爆破炮 發射
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.28,0:14:27.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光子爆破炮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.17,0:14:29.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發射
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.70,0:14:49.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.64,0:14:52.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經是位合格的艦長了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.13,0:15:00.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來會是個漫長的假期
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.73,0:15:16.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舍利奇機信號消失…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.79,0:15:38.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天神號最大戰速
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.73,0:15:40.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突破敵人防線
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.88,0:15:42.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最大戰速
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.40,0:15:45.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,航向 敵人要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.89,0:16:00.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼感覺？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.16,0:16:08.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.19,0:16:14.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狄恩？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.92,0:16:16.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狄恩 是你嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.21,0:16:18.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉歐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.01,0:16:27.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 為什麼你會在機動戰士裏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.58,0:16:29.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.25,0:16:32.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我向露烏保證過
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.50,0:16:36.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會帶她去地球
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.82,0:16:38.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.14,0:16:42.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算對手是你 我也不在乎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.07,0:16:47.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我說 狄恩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.82,0:16:50.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要大家互相體諒 不用戰爭也…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.91,0:16:52.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是猴年馬月的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.34,0:16:54.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天？明天？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.21,0:16:56.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年後？一百年後？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.31,0:16:57.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.59,0:17:00.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說只有趁自己…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.69,0:17:03.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還活著的時候 賭眼前這場戰爭…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.27,0:17:09.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.51,0:17:20.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.33,0:17:23.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.57,0:17:26.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想看到再有人死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.83,0:17:30.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想看到大家都好好地活著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.47,0:17:35.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭我沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.76,0:17:37.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恨我也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.36,0:17:41.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我想讓狄恩活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.08,0:17:44.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉歐…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.99,0:17:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.89,0:17:58.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…想在地球上風景最美的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.45,0:18:01.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為露烏立一座墓碑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.20,0:18:08.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四周 開滿她最愛的花兒 漫山遍野
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.22,0:18:11.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放眼望去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.67,0:18:15.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鏡子般的湖面 延伸到天邊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.89,0:18:19.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉歐也會…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.88,0:18:22.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時常來看露烏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.49,0:18:26.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了 狄恩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.82,0:18:29.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉歐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.02,0:18:58.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來還是要我親自出馬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.33,0:18:59.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高達
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.01,0:19:02.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就送你歸西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.99,0:19:06.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.42,0:19:09.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要把狄恩…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.92,0:19:11.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是自己人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.71,0:19:14.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去戰鬥力的機動戰士就是一堆廢鐵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.23,0:19:17.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只不過是在清理垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.62,0:19:20.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我的手裏 讓它廢物利用
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.60,0:19:22.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為一堆垃圾 也該心滿意足了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.45,0:19:50.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無謂的掙扎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.22,0:19:51.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.83,0:20:37.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可饒恕…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.50,0:20:43.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕不饒你！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.95,0:21:24.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕不饒你！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.88,0:21:30.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.60,0:21:31.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.17,0:21:37.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該死的地球種
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.78,0:21:51.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各部隊 報告損失
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.76,0:21:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薩那倫多部隊 傷亡慘重
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.83,0:21:57.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要塞防線有崩潰跡象
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.71,0:21:59.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人艦隊開始發起突擊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.13,0:22:02.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投入所有預備隊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.80,0:22:04.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別讓他們輕而易舉突破
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.78,0:22:05.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.93,0:22:10.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今我還在猶豫什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.10,0:22:13.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連同敵人艦隊一起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.01,0:22:16.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,排除所有妨礙計劃的人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.18,0:22:20.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 無論如何…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.61,0:22:23.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須抵達伊甸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.01,0:23:59.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逝去的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.09,0:24:02.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是傑哈特實現野心的代價嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.39,0:24:05.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 機動戰士高達AGE
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.03,0:24:07.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕望之光
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.35,0:24:11.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三個人的命運成就歷史

